着凌夜大叫，众人汗~\r<br>接下来……后果不堪而想，凌夜就这样给虐了……\r<br>--------------------回忆完毕-----------------------------\r<br>“咳~我怎么会有这样的亲戚。”凌夜彪悍\r<br>“可是，问题是，夕恋不是你妹妹么？为啥%……？”尹月沉思着\r<br>“这个……我要是知道就好了，她也是我亲生妹啊！为什么。”\r<br>“恩，看起来，结论只有一个了！”涵抱着头，说\r<br>“什么，快说快说。”众人十分着急……八卦啦……\r<br>“那个什么皆明的一定是个同性恋！BL！”众人听了，包括凌夜也点点头……\r<br>“啊！那我们班上的男生岂不是……”\r<br>“有可能哦！小李子、凌夜！月！”\u0018","author":"秘密的小秘密","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.68ffb7b8.DOFD1BRiNXYzC6XiPJgupA&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-18 15:57","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":28,"title":"回复：【原创】梦","content":"sf.","author":"月_少年","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.d529c65b.ayJyCEXSVtAXpFPLcaQg6Q?t=1594050772&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-18 15:57","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":29,"title":"回复：【原创】梦","content":".....=&nbsp;=\r<br>\r<br>这到底是啥啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！\r<br>\r<br>...BL放在这里...专门被批的.","author":"月_少年","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.d529c65b.ayJyCEXSVtAXpFPLcaQg6Q?t=1594050772&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-18 15:59","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":30,"title":"回复：【原创】梦","content":"热爱……\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>热爱BL……\r<br>\r<br>BL不是罪！\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>不过声明：我不是BL@！","author":"秘密的小秘密","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.68ffb7b8.DOFD1BRiNXYzC6XiPJgupA&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-18 20:01","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":31,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】梦","content":"....","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-18 20:04","ip":null,"old_image":"http://hiphotos.baidu.com/%5F%5F%5F%5F%E7%CD%B6%F9/pic/item/5d5ae9590ef0949d810a1822.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":32,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】梦","content":"D","author":"秘密的小秘密","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.68ffb7b8.DOFD1BRiNXYzC6XiPJgupA&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-19 14:28","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":33,"title":"回复：回复：